<section class="hero"><div class="hero-inner"><div class="breadcrumb"><a href="index.html">SFGS</a> <span>/</span> Admission <span>/</span> How To Apply</div><h2>How To <em>Apply</em></h2><div class="hero-divider"></div><p class="hero-tagline">Six clear steps from filling the form to receiving your admission letter — start your SFGS journey today.</p></div></section>
<div class="motto-strip"><span class="star">★</span><p>Apply · Test · Interview · Enrol</p><span class="star">★</span></div>
<div class="main-wrap"><main class="content">
<div class="apply-intro">
  <h3>"Begin your SFGS journey today."</h3>
  <p>St Francis Girls Suwerwa is one of the most prestigious schools in Kenya, with a reputation for academic excellence and the holistic development of its students. Below are the comprehensive guidelines on how to apply for admission.</p>
</div>

<h2 class="section-heading">Step-by-Step Application Process</h2>

<div class="steps-container">

  <div class="step">
    <div class="step-num">1</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h3><span class="step-icon">📋</span>Obtain the Application Form</h3>
      <p>The first step is to obtain the official application form. You may collect it directly from St Francis Girls Suwerwa, or download it from the school's website. Complete the form accurately and legibly, providing all required information including bio-data, academic records, and personal information.</p>
      <span class="step-meta">📥 Available Online or On-Site</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <div class="step-num">2</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h3><span class="step-icon">💳</span>Pay the Application Fee</h3>
      <p>Upon completing the application form, candidates must pay a <strong>non-refundable application fee</strong>. Payment can be made via bank deposit or electronic payment. The bank account details and full payment options will be provided together with the application form.</p>
      <span class="step-meta">💰 Non-refundable Fee</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <div class="step-num">3</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h3><span class="step-icon">📤</span>Submit Your Application</h3>
      <p>Submit the completed application form, academic records, and supporting documents to the school's admissions office.</p>
      <strong style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--navy);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif">Supporting Documents Required:</strong>
      <div class="docs-required">
        <div class="doc-required">Completed application form</div>
        <div class="doc-required">Certified copy of birth certificate</div>
        <div class="doc-required">Recommendation letter from current school</div>
        <div class="doc-required">Two passport-size photographs</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <div class="step-num">4</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h3><span class="step-icon">📝</span>Sit the Entrance Examination</h3>
      <p>After submission, candidates will be required to sit for an entrance examination — mandatory for all applicants. The exam assesses academic ability and suitability for SFGS's rigorous curriculum.</p>
      <strong style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--navy);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif">Exam Subjects:</strong>
      <div class="exam-subjects">
        <div class="exam-chip"><span class="icon">📐</span>Mathematics</div>
        <div class="exam-chip"><span class="icon">📖</span>English</div>
        <div class="exam-chip"><span class="icon">🔬</span>General Science</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <div class="step-num">5</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h3><span class="step-icon">🎤</span>Attend the Interview</h3>
      <p>Candidates who perform well in the entrance examination will be invited for an interview, typically conducted by a panel of school officials. The interview assesses interpersonal skills, leadership potential, and other non-academic attributes that are critical for success at St Francis Girls Suwerwa.</p>
      <span class="step-meta">👥 Panel Interview</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <div class="step-num">6</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h3><span class="step-icon">🎉</span>Receive Your Admission Decision</h3>
      <p>Finally, successful candidates will be notified of their admission status and offered a place at St Francis Girls Suwerwa. The admission letter will include the fee structure, reporting date, and details on what to bring on the first day.</p>
      <span class="step-meta">🏆 Welcome to SFGS!</span>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<div class="checklist-banner">
  <h3>✅ Pre-Application Checklist</h3>
  <p style="font-size:.92rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:1rem;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif">Make sure you have these ready before starting your application:</p>
  <div class="checklist-grid">
    <div class="checklist-item"><span class="check">✓</span> Birth certificate (certified copy)</div>
    <div class="checklist-item"><span class="check">✓</span> Recent academic records</div>
    <div class="checklist-item"><span class="check">✓</span> School recommendation letter</div>
    <div class="checklist-item"><span class="check">✓</span> Two passport-size photographs</div>
    <div class="checklist-item"><span class="check">✓</span> Application fee payment</div>
    <div class="checklist-item"><span class="check">✓</span> Parent/Guardian contact details</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="final-cta">
  <h3>Ready to Start Your Journey?</h3>
  <p>Have questions about the application process? Our admissions team is ready to help.</p>
  <a href="contact.html" class="btn">Contact Admissions →</a>
</div>
